         <div type="translation"
              ana="#b1"
              xml:id="zoor0307.translation"
              corresp="#zoor0307.transcription">
            <p>One (is) the God, the Lord of all. Monument of Saoreos, who died having a good
                    name and good faith (at the age) of 27 years, in the year... [on (the) .. (day)
                    of (the) month] Audynaios, [on (the) . day of (the) Lord. Be of good cheer, no
                    one (is) immortal].</p>
         </div>
